Title: Angel of Death
Plot: When Jenny returns from her European trip, the entire NCIS team will be forced to take a Homeland Security polygraph test, and the deepest secrets of each agent are about to be revealed. Plus, an unarmed Tony and Jeanne are held hostage by a ruthless drug dealer.
GuestStars: Armand Assante, Scottie Thompson, Alan Smyth, Mike Erwin, Shelly Cole, Brian Dietzen, Liza Lapira, David Dayan Fisher, Marcy Harriell, Sandra Thigpen, Stephanie Mello, Roxana Brusso, Dayo Ade, Joe Spano
